## **Shared Strapi slug utilities (app-wide)**

| Utility | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| [`unwrapStrapiRecord`](mdc:src/lib/strapi/unwrapRecord.ts) | Flatten v4 `attributes` / v5 flattened records |
| [`unwrapStrapiRelation`](mdc:src/lib/strapi/unwrapRecord.ts) | Unwrap `data`-nested relations |
| [`normalizeStrapiSlug`](mdc:src/lib/strapi/unwrapRecord.ts) / [`findByStrapiSlug`](mdc:src/lib/strapi/unwrapRecord.ts) | Case-insensitive in-memory slug match |
| [`fetchStrapiEntryBySlug`](mdc:src/lib/strapi/fetchBySlug.ts) | Direct `$eqi` fetch + list fallback for collection types |

Re-exported from [`src/lib/strapi.ts`](mdc:src/lib/strapi.ts). Use these in **mosc-redesign** CMS modules (saints, publications, kalpana, directory, etc.) instead of one-off slug logic.

Optional Strapi-side cleanup: normalize edition slugs to match URLs (`kalpana-2025` not `kalpana-2025-mo2`). **Frontend fallbacks remain required** for legacy/imported suffixes.

