## **Checklist (news integration)**

- [ ] Category fetches use `STRAPI_NEWS_CATEGORY_SLUGS` + `buildCategorySlugFilter`
- [ ] Default operator is `$eq` after Strapi slug backfill on Cloud
- [ ] Article detail links use API `slug` unchanged
- [ ] Tenant + published filters on every article list
- [ ] Section anchor IDs (`#main-news`) are UI-only; they are not Strapi filter values

## **Checklist (parent/child CMS pages — Kalpana and similar)**

- [ ] Parent lookup: slug `$eqi` → semantic key (year, etc.) → list match → defaults/synthesize
- [ ] Child lookup: `filters[parent][slug][$eqi]` → if empty, `filters[parent][year][$eq]` (or equivalent)
- [ ] Tenant filter on every request; never drop tenant on 200 + empty
- [ ] Unwrap records with `unwrapStrapiRecord` before reading fields
- [ ] Detail route: avoid 404 when child data exists but parent slug differs in Strapi
- [ ] Verify empty state against API with **year/parent key**, not URL slug alone

